        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer818442281" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17951663049431973449">There&apos;s a reason why Gabriel Garcia Marquez learned Catalan just read to this novel. He called it &quot;the most beautiful novel published in Spain since the Civil War.&quot; <br/><br/>Great translation by poet David Rosenthal that captures the gorgeously off-handed rhythms and glowing repetitions of Rodereda&apos;s prose. Avoid the newer version called &quot;In Diamond Plaza.&quot; </span>
  <span id="freeText17951663049431973449" style="display:none">There's a reason why Gabriel Garcia Marquez learned Catalan just read to this novel. He called it "the most beautiful novel published in Spain since the Civil War." <br /><br />Great translation by poet David Rosenthal that captures the gorgeously off-handed rhythms and glowing repetitions of Rodereda's prose. Avoid the newer version called "In Diamond Plaza." </span>
