  <span id="freeText3998475492969973185" style="display:none">I'm a little speechless, a little breathless. <i>The Time of the Doves</i> is one of the most beautiful things I've encountered in a long time. I'm overwhelmed; I need a moment. I don't know. Read this book.</span>
